{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8b09170edf","title":"中共中央、中央文革重要通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d75d580b3d","index":0,"year":1968,"month":5,"day":18,"articleId":"8b09170edf"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"92a8a42842","name":"姚文元","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","name":"中共党史教学参考资料 第26册 “文化大革命”参考资料 中册（1988年）","internal":true,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"},{"id":"45f848c5df","name":"姚文元"}]},"publication_details":{"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dc2720891b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席批示：照发中共中央、中央文革","index":0,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"8b09170edf"},{"id":"eec21c0a88","type":"paragraph","text":"重要通知","index":1,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"8b09170edf"},{"id":"5ae5a2980a","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六八年五月十八日）","index":2,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"8b09170edf"},{"id":"a2e48da765","type":"paragraph","text":"最近毛主席批评了在一个文件中用了“世界革命的中心——北京”这种提法。毛主席再一饮指出：“这种话不应由中国人口中说出，这就是所调“以我为核心”的错误思想。”","index":3,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"8b09170edf"},{"id":"6d67e6d326","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的批评，应引起各级党、政、军、群及驻外使馆的注意。毛主席的指示，我们应坚决贯彻执行，今后，不论在报刊上（包括各种小报），在内部文件中，在各种讲话中，特别在接待外宾时，一律不要再用“世界革命的中心”的这种说法。对于“以我为核心”的错误思想，应经常警竭和批判。","index":4,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"8b09170edf"},{"id":"2a42bcf57d","type":"paragraph","text":"文元同志","index":5,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"8b09170edf"},{"id":"8ab63478fd","type":"paragraph","text":"建议此件批发全国，先印若干份，分发有关同志，然后在碰头会上宣读一次，加以修改，再加批语发出，在我看过的同类材料中，此件是写得量好的","index":6,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"8b09170edf"},{"id":"62e60f8f9a","type":"paragraph","text":"此厂情况，我已从个别同志那里听过两次，你是否可以去那里一看，问一问？","index":7,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"8b09170edf"},{"id":"c29d9aab6e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":8,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"8b09170edf"},{"id":"30588a3d7c","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十九日呈主席参阅此件总结了消理队伍中一些政策性问题","index":9,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"8b09170edf"},{"id":"ef3c9feaf9","type":"paragraph","text":"姚文元","index":10,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"8b09170edf"},{"id":"7672021618","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十三日","index":11,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"8b09170edf"},{"id":"6be76402b8","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央、中央文革转发毛主席关于《北京新华印刷厂军管会发动群众开展对敌斗争的","index":12,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"8b09170edf"},{"id":"48316b44ff","type":"paragraph","text":"经验》的批示的通知","index":13,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"8b09170edf"},{"id":"c9ccec81de","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六八年五月二十五日）","index":14,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"8b09170edf"}],"page":{"id":"0d70f4804f","publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"8b09170edf","start":139,"end":139}}}},"__N_SSG":true}